section.def:
on-site user (到場使用者) means a person inspecting or obtaining documents and
                    information specified in items 1, 2, 4, 6 and 7 of Part 2 of this
                        Schedule at the office for the registration of companies;

paragraph.content:
a company that was, at any time before the commencement date of
                                Part 16 of the Ordinance, registered in the register kept
                            under section 333AA of the predecessor Ordinance;

section.def:
subsequent account (其後帳户) means any account, other than the
                    principal account, that a registered online user registers with the Registrar
                    under a registration arrangement;
